      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.90dayanswers.com/?p=181</guid>
      <description>I love the p90x workout calendar! Does anyone know how to shrink the calendar? I&amp;#8217;d like to print a bunch of these and place them around my house and in my book bag. This way, I will run into them all day and it will keep me aware of my workouts everyday. I think that [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/90-day-answers/90_Day_Answers-P90X_Workout_Calendar.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I love the p90x workout calendar! Does anyone know how to shrink the calendar? I&#8217;d like to print a bunch of these and place them around my house and in my book bag. This way, I will run into them all day and it will keep me aware of my workouts everyday. I think that this will keep me motivated and excited about my upcoming workouts. P90x is intense and I like to look at the materials often to &#8220;ease the pain&#8221; haha.</p>
