      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Is it normal to be so tired and beat up after taking the p90x fitness test? I just did it and I think I might die. Actually, I think I&#8217;m already dead. How am I supposed to get through the normal workouts if I can&#8217;t even get through the dangety darn fitness test. P90x is going to kick my tail. Is there a not so extreme fitness program that I can follow so that I can be in good enough shape for p90x?</p>
